body:
Hey Avicadians,

Today I bring you a more alternative game: Write your name backwards, then comment on the name above!
So yea...
Very self explanatory, but for those who haven't got the jist yet.
  1. Write your name backwards.
  2. Is it weird? Confusing? Or just plain gibberish?
  3. Rate the person's *backwards* name above you, out of 10.
Simple....... Right?

 _mezzilB

Pretty cool.
